      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves and get ready for a rewarding project with this budget-friendly find! While this vehicle currently shows significant wear and will require some mechanical attention and bodywork to get back to its best, it's the perfect canvas for a car enthusiast or a DIY mechanic looking for a great deal. If you're looking for an affordable way to get started on a restoration journey, this is the one for you!",
