    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly with no unusual noises, and the transmission shifts reliably through all gears. While the interior is clean and the electronics are fully functional, you may find some minor cosmetic wear on the upholstery and a few small scratches on the exterior paint consistent with regular use. It serves as a dependable daily driver that requires no immediate mechanical attention.",
