    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly immaculate, mint condition, appearing as though it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and the interior is pristine, showing absolutely no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. A buyer can expect a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives like new, with all features functioning exactly as intended.",
