      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for this awesome ride. It\u2019s been super reliable and is still in really solid shape, perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without the 'new car' price tag. It runs great and has been well-loved! Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 29500.0,
